<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4634565>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Copulatory organs and bursal appendages of the representatives of group 1A. A, T. venenosum: A1, 3 copulatory organ; A2, 4 bursal appendage. (A1, 2 specimen from Norway, neotype; A3,4 specimen from Sardinia). B, T. messoplanoides: B1 copulatory organ; B2 bursal appendage. (from the holotype; after Artois et al., 2000)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4634565/files/figure.png" .

